Rapunzel is ready to go on the most exciting adventure of her life. Now, you want to ask us, why? She has got the admission in her favorite college and today is the first day to join it. The princess is known for her unique fashion designer abilities, but today she looks confused what to wear. Will you give your helping hands to the cutest girl of this universe? Join Rapunzel Modern College Fashion and get ready to help her prepare for the first day of classes!

The good news is that her wardrobe is full of fabulous teen school outfits, new hairstyles and designer handbags. All you need to do is just put your unique fashion sense to challenge to help the lovely princess look gorgeous. You can also find out the best cosmetics in her wardrobe. Put on a pink color frock, or blue top and red color skirt or a white color frock with wide pink dot in this brand new dressing game for girls! Choose a nice matching spectacle, and a purse or a mobile phone or a tablet to complete her look!

Once you are done, do not forget to click the Show button to see the final result of this cool html5 princess dress-up game! We are delighted to offer different types of doll dress up kids games for free to play online. Stays connected with us to spot new girls dressing game and have fun to the fullest, no download required!
